  "detailed_description": "<strong>Fight against Monsters</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/1f111cfea7918c4463f9c58d301e5e46.poster.avif?t=1766178979\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/1f111cfea7918c4463f9c58d301e5e46.webm?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/1f111cfea7918c4463f9c58d301e5e46.mp4?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In each game, you'll face numerous attacking monsters. Fight against them and survive for as long as possible.<br><br><strong>Power Up the Character</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/4801dbbccd6cf528a6105e85d27fe6aa.poster.avif?t=1766178979\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/4801dbbccd6cf528a6105e85d27fe6aa.webm?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/4801dbbccd6cf528a6105e85d27fe6aa.mp4?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As you defeat a certain number of monsters, your character will level up and have the opportunity to choose a magic item.<br><br><strong>Craft Items</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/b700179e636f08f37796ffb327f08672.poster.avif?t=1766178979\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/b700179e636f08f37796ffb327f08672.webm?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/b700179e636f08f37796ffb327f08672.mp4?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You also have the ability to craft items with woods.<br><br><strong>Defeat the Final Boss</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/80cc3c91c9d42e79a77e37aa0e175e34.poster.avif?t=1766178979\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/80cc3c91c9d42e79a77e37aa0e175e34.webm?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/80cc3c91c9d42e79a77e37aa0e175e34.mp4?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Survive for a specific duration and face the final boss and claim victory by defeating it.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Fight against Monsters</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/1f111cfea7918c4463f9c58d301e5e46.poster.avif?t=1766178979\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/1f111cfea7918c4463f9c58d301e5e46.webm?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/1f111cfea7918c4463f9c58d301e5e46.mp4?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In each game, you'll face numerous attacking monsters. Fight against them and survive for as long as possible.<br><br><strong>Power Up the Character</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/4801dbbccd6cf528a6105e85d27fe6aa.poster.avif?t=1766178979\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/4801dbbccd6cf528a6105e85d27fe6aa.webm?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/4801dbbccd6cf528a6105e85d27fe6aa.mp4?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As you defeat a certain number of monsters, your character will level up and have the opportunity to choose a magic item.<br><br><strong>Craft Items</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/b700179e636f08f37796ffb327f08672.poster.avif?t=1766178979\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/b700179e636f08f3